title: Bat Lash 1-6 (of 06) (2008) (Minutemen-Mantooth)
description:
Bat Lash 1-6 (of 06) (2008) (Minutemen-Mantooth)

Written by Peter Brandvold and Sergio Aragones; Art by John Severin; Cover by Nick Cardy and Kevin Nowlan

The acclaimed 6-issue Western miniseries that brought back Bat Lash is collected in this torrent! 
In it, young Bat must face a crooked sheriff intent on destroying his family name and save the woman he loves.
